MAP: 这个ADT适合: 有一集合的元素, 要对每个元素进行处理

1. have a set of elements to process:   e.g. [64 floats]
2. function to run on each element:     e.g. ["square"]

MAP(elements, function) 

GPUs are good at map:
1. GPUs have many parallel processors
2. GPUs optimize for throughput

e.g. Problems that can be solved using a Map: 
1. sort an input array ❌
2. add one to each element in an input array ✅： parallel computing
3. sum up all elements in an input array ❌ 
4. compute the average of an input array ❌ 

只要不是每个element独立处理: 都是CPU擅长而不是GPU
